{"tid":1092260,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"]一週年紀念！各足協、媒體紛紛發文致敬C朗經典倒鉤","createTime":"2019-04-04T16:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T09:52:28.000Z","uid":173952,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"ffd604c1b825a64d97752a353980c7fe92015be7","tid":1092260,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T16:29:43.000Z","msg":"一年前的歐冠1/4決賽首回合，C羅兩射一傳幫助皇馬3-0客勝尤文，這也是皇馬自1962年以來首次在客場擊敗尤文。<br />\n<br />\n比賽下半場葡萄牙巨星打進了一粒相當精彩的進球：C羅接馬塞洛長傳，自己過人、自己組織了一次快速反擊，最終C羅接卡瓦哈爾傳中，在點球點附近高高躍起，打進了一粒絕世倒鉤！<br />\n<br />\n這粒倒鉤離地2.38米，動作極其舒展，騰空高度極高，布馮毫無反應。隨後尤文球迷紛紛起立並為對手C羅鼓掌，齊達內震驚地摸頭甩手，而布馮也向C羅豎起了大拇指。 C羅本人在看到尤文球迷的鼓掌後，停止慶祝並微微躬身感謝球迷們。<br />\n<br />\n在C羅經典倒鉤一周年之際，國際足聯、歐足聯、葡萄牙國家隊、露天看台，BT sports，Goal等各大賬號紛紛發文，致敬尤文巨星的這一經典進球。"},{"pid":"76ebc267c116e2254a7c90ac69ee1130683aec92","tid":1092260,"uid":173952,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T16:30:15.000Z","msg":"唔會過2頁"},{"pid":"e0ab8aaf54c3dda1649dec3eb1039127e4c61c80","tid":1092260,"uid":34993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76ebc267c116e2254a7c90ac69ee1130683aec92","tid":1092260,"uid":173952,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T16:30:15.000Z","msg":"唔會過2頁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T16:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3feb4b565196c48e8ab1d93baf20bafd5d3cc46","tid":1092260,"uid":18646,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76ebc267c116e2254a7c90ac69ee1130683aec92","tid":1092260,"uid":173952,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T16:30:15.000Z","msg":"唔會過2頁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T16:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 